slightly to maintain good element quality. In the target region, we generate tetrahedral and voxel elements using the background grids. (c)We insert tetrahedral elements between the elements of diÔ¨Äerent
sizes to maintain the integrity of the mesh. InÔ¨Ånite elements are generated on the sides and bottom of
the model.
